articles.title: Austria to phase out AstraZeneca coronavirus vaccine - Moneycontrol
articles.description: Austria becomes the third European country to drop AstraZeneca, after Norway and Denmark ditched the vaccine over rare cases of severe blood clots in people receiving the jab.
